Memory - A Memory Game in Python & Pygame

Released under a "Simplified BSD" license

This game can run with both Python 2 and Python 3. This game is featured in the book "Making Games with Python & Pygame" by Al Sweigart. This book is released under a Creative Commons licenses and can be downloaded from http://inventwithpython.com/pygame

The obfuscated version is, from the Python interpreter's point of view, the exact same program as the normal game. This just demonstrates that readability is for the programmer's sake, and makes modifying or updating the code much easier.

Game Instructions:

Select matching tiles until you have found them all.